                    Specifies the value whose bits to count.
                </p></dd></dl></div></div><div class="refsect1"><a id="description"></a><h2>Description</h2><p>
            <code class="function">bitCount</code> returns the number of bits that are set to 1 in the binary representation of <em class="parameter"><code>value</code></em>.
